  "title": "Sales Executive (Electrical)",
  "description": "<p><p>Our client is a <strong>Electrical, and Electronics Manufacturing.  </strong>Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a  <strong>Sales Executive</strong> to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the  <strong>West  </strong>- easily accessible.<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br /><br /><strong>Sales Generation:</strong> Support team revenue growth by managing all stages of the sales process, including lead generation, responding to customer inquiries, processing orders, and providing post-sales support.</p></p><p><p><strong>Customer Relationship Management:</strong> Build and maintain strong relationships with existing and prospective customers by delivering prompt, accurate information, addressing concerns, and ensuring overall satisfaction.</p></p><p><p><strong>Proposal and Quotation Preparation:</strong> Prepare accurate sales proposals and quotations, ensuring timely delivery to customers.</p></p><p><p><strong>Market Research:</strong> Analyze market trends, competitor activity, and customer needs to identify sales opportunities and inform effective sales strategies.</p></p><p><p><strong>Trade Shows and Events:</strong> Assist in planning, coordinating, and executing trade shows, industry events, and product demonstrations to showcase offerings and engage customers.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate with experience in the electrical background is preferred. </li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em></p><p><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em></p><p><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em></p><p><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p></p>",
